about_me.des: I'm an Android developer, and interested in ReactiveX(Rx) and Open Source. I'm always thinking how to make my codes come to be clean code with strong architecture. Life is continuous learning. I have to practice to be professional through the learning. That's why Skateboarding and DJing turning into my hobby, and Video Production is my new hobby.
